                        qphix-codegen testsuite
                        =======================

 Rudimentary test framework to test the arch specific intrinsics
 declared in instructions.h. The test framework constitutes of 
 three portions. 
 
   A) generate_test.cc : Uses the same basic design as the codegen.cc. 
      Conatains a specific function generate_FnXXX() to generate a
      header file for each of the FnXXX() declared in instructions.h.
                        
   B) test_gen_fnXXX.h : Test headers generated by the generate_test.cc.
   
   C) run_tests.cc     : Executes the test cases by comparing the 
      test_gen_fnXXX.h function definition to a corresponding C function.
  

To add new tests for the instructions.h intrinsics:

a) Add a new generate_FnXXX() function to generate_test.cc. Note this 
   would generate the testcase (test_gen_fnXXX.h) file.

b) Add a new test_xxx() fuction to run_tests.cc.

For both cases do not forget to add the new functions to the main().
 
